### Instructions to Use:

#### 1. Go to your backend folder:

```bash
cd faculty-finder-app/server
```

#### 2. Create this file:

You can create it manually or overwrite any existing `package.json` with the above content.

#### 3. Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

This will install:

* Express (backend framework)
* MySQL (for DB connection)
* Cors (to allow frontend requests)
* Body-parser (to read POST data)

#### 4. Run the backend:

```bash
npm start
```

